{"tid":1562011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"祖國大規模停水停電 有住院患者死亡","createTime":"2019-09-12T00:10:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T00:26:01.000Z","uid":43041,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fd4a30935353e8cc6b4dac8dc991a58d3333c8c8","tid":1562011,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:10:42.000Z","msg":"法西颱風9日重創我國，千葉縣10日仍有大範圍地區停水、停電，導致印西市1名住院男患者死亡。由於倒塌的電線桿、送電鷹架等搶修費時，29萬戶還不知何時才能恢復供電。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JKoZNEP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJKoZNEP.jpg&h=1df343fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n千葉的西佐倉印西醫院1名62歲住院患者2016年因腦中風住院，9日凌晨突然呼吸不順，院方緊急抽痰後仍不治死亡。<br />\n<br />\n千葉縣醫療整備課指出，該醫院沒有自家發電設施，患者呼吸困難是否與停電有關仍有待調查。<br />\n<br />\n君津市的鈴木醫院因停電無法照顧99名住院患者，已緊急將患者送往其他醫院。<br />\n<br />\n千葉縣警方指出，受到停電影響，千葉縣至10日上午5時至少有339個十字路口的紅綠燈不亮。目前已在交通量大且事故危險性高的地方設置發電機，或派警員前往指揮交通。"},{"pid":"f66b62d791683a65f1721b04af59b05e90e99d5d","tid":1562011,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:11:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a4bcc7a994049265774cc38edb281cd751bc687","tid":1562011,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T00:11:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"2a652fc